WEBVTT

1
00:08:20.140 --> 00:08:23.090 
但他们都会交朋友  不是吗
But they all make friends, though, don't they?

2
00:08:23.270 --> 00:08:25.380 
伙伴
Companions?

3
00:08:25.980 --> 00:08:28.280 
别说了  不许笑
Stop it! Stop laughing!

4
00:08:28.280 --> 00:08:31.860 
你甚至可以说你变成了他的配对
You might even say you became his counterpart,

5
00:08:31.860 --> 00:08:34.770 
变成了某种
might say you became kind of a...

6
00:08:35.370 --> 00:08:36.690 
镜像
Reflection.

7
00:08:37.370 --> 00:08:38.480 
我讨厌你
I hate you!

8
00:08:38.750 --> 00:08:40.940 
我不  我不在乎
I don't -- I don't care.

9
00:08:41.870 --> 00:08:43.610 
怎么  你以为自己自由了吗
What? Did you think you're free?

10
00:08:43.670 --> 00:08:45.920 
以为自己逃脱了吗
That -- that you escaped?

11
00:08:45.920 --> 00:08:48.360 
你现在被困在火车上了
You're stuck on the train now.

12
00:08:48.510 --> 00:08:50.550 
你只是在另一面镜子里
You're just in another mirror.

13
00:08:50.550 --> 00:08:51.580 
不
No.

